<concept id="id_4" class="- topic/topic concept/concept "><title class="- topic/title ">Create a BDD test case with Cucumber hooks</title><conbody class="- topic/body  concept/conbody "><ol class="- topic/ol "><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">To create a BDD test case with Cucumber hooks in <ph conkeyref="name-variables/katalon-studio" class="- topic/ph "/>, first, you need to set up Cucumber hooks in <ph conkeyref="name-variables/katalon-studio" class="- topic/ph "/>. See <xref href="../../Manage_Test_Artifacts/Working_With_BDD_Feature_File/set_up_cucumber_hooks.dita" class="- topic/xref ">Set up Cucumber hooks</xref>.</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Create a new test case. You can refer to this document: <xref href="../Create_A_New_Test_Case/Create_a_new_test_case.dita" class="- topic/xref ">Create a new test case in <ph conkeyref="name-variables/katalon-studio" class="- topic/ph "/></xref>.</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">In the <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Manual</uicontrol> view of the new test case, click on the <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Add</uicontrol> dropdown button and select <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Cucumber Keywords</uicontrol>.</p><p class="- topic/p "><image href="https://github.com/katalon-studio/docs-images/raw/master/katalon-studio/docs/cucumber-test-hooks/KS-Add-Cucumber-keyword.png" scope="external" width="700" class="- topic/image "><alt class="- topic/alt ">Add Cucumber Keywords</alt></image></p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Select the <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Run Feature File</uicontrol> keyword.</p><p class="- topic/p "><image href="https://github.com/katalon-studio/docs-images/raw/master/katalon-studio/docs/cucumber-test-hooks/KS-select-run-feature-file-keyword.png" scope="external" width="700" class="- topic/image "><alt class="- topic/alt ">Select Run Feature File keyword</alt></image></p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">To get the relative path, right-click on the Feature file and select <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Copy ID</uicontrol>.</p><p class="- topic/p "><image href="https://github.com/katalon-studio/docs-images/raw/master/katalon-studio/docs/cucumber-test-hooks/KS-Copy-ID-feature-file.png" scope="external" width="400" class="- topic/image "><alt class="- topic/alt ">Copy ID of Feature file</alt></image></p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Double-click on the <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Input</uicontrol> cell of the <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Run Feature File</uicontrol> keyword. In the displayed <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Input</uicontrol> dialog, paste the copied relative path from step 3 as the input value.</p><p class="- topic/p "><image href="https://github.com/katalon-studio/docs-images/raw/master/katalon-studio/docs/cucumber-test-hooks/KS-Feature-file-input-value.png" scope="external" width="700" class="- topic/image "><alt class="- topic/alt ">Paste keyword input value</alt></image></p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Run the test and verify the message of the Cucumber hooks in the <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Console</uicontrol> log:</p><p class="- topic/p "><image href="https://github.com/katalon-studio/docs-images/raw/master/katalon-studio/docs/cucumber-test-hooks/KS-Cucumber-hooks-message.png" scope="external" width="700" class="- topic/image "><alt class="- topic/alt ">Cucumber hooks message</alt></image></p></li></ol></conbody></concept>